<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .logo { color: #4F46E5; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; }
    .message-box { background: #f7f9fc; border: 1px solid #e3e8ef; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #6B7280; }
    .sender-info { margin-bottom: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">The Gross Profit Podcast</div>
      <p>New Message from a Podcast Website Visitor</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Dear <%= @profile.name %>,</p>
    
    <p>You've received a message through The Gross Profit Podcast website. Someone is interested in connecting with you!</p>
    
    <div class="sender-info">
      <p><strong>From:</strong> <%= @guest_message.sender_name %> (<%= @guest_message.sender_email %>)</p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= @guest_message.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
      <% if @guest_message.subject.present? %>
        <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= @guest_message.subject %></p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    
    <div class="message-box">
      <h3>Message:</h3>
      <p><%= simple_format @guest_message.message %></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>You can reply directly to this email to respond to <%= @guest_message.sender_name %>.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Gross Profit Podcast Team</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This message was sent to you because you are a guest on The Gross Profit Podcast. If you would like to opt out of receiving future messages from podcast visitors, please contact us.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.today.year %> The Gross Profit Podcast. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>